snippet.title: Reignfall Trailer
snippet.description:
Get the game: https://store.steampowered.com/app/935930/Reignfall/

Reignfall is a real-time strategy game with elements of city-building and third-person action. Build a city and defend it against waves of increasingly difficult enemies. Fight against the fallen hordes by commanding your armies RTS-style or take direct control of your heroes in third person and personally fight along side your troops on the battlefield.
